    "media:imagetext": "Effective Nov. 27, 1967\nAIR\nCALIFORNIA\nSERVING SAN FRANCISCO, OAKLAND,\nSAN JOSE AND THE ORANGE COUNTY\nDISNEYLAND AREA\nMovieland\nWax Museum\nRiverside\nFreeway\nKnott's\nBerry Farm\nAnaheim\nDisneyland\nSanta\nGarden\nGrove\nFreeway\nAngels Baseball Stadium\n122\nFreeway\nPacific\nBeach Blvd.\nSanta Ana\nHarbor Bivd\nHuntington Beach\nCoast\nNewport Freeway\nOrange County\nAirport\nUniversity\nof California\nIrvine\nNewport •\nBeach\nHighway\nEl Toro\nMarine Base\nSanta\nCatalina\nIsland\n• Avalon\nLaguna Beach\nFLY THE EASY WAY\nEliminate long freeway excursions at both ends of\nyour flight between the Bay Area and Orange Coun-\nty/Disneyland. Now you can fly over Los Angeles to\nthe heart of Orange County aboard an Air California\nElectra-Jet.\nAir California Electra-Jet Service\nis easy on your Pocket Book.\n1485\nONE-WAY PLUS TAX",
